headline: Henry Schein to Webcast Second Quarter 2025 Conference Call on Tuesday, August 5, 2025, at 8:00 a.m. ET
summary: MELVILLE, N.Y., July 22, 2025--Henry Schein, Inc. (Nasdaq: HSIC), the world’s largest provider of health care solutions to office-based dental and medical practitioners, announced today that it will release its second quarter 2025 financial results before the stock market opens on Tuesday, August 5, 2025, and will provide a live webcast of its earnings conference call on the same day beginning at 8:00 a.m. Eastern time. Speakers on the call will include Stanley M. Bergman, Chairman of the Board
